0.1.1
- Initial release as Miner's Blueprint.
- Added 3D selection flow:
  - Key 1 sets start point from looked object/hit position.
  - Key 2 sets end point and builds a green world-space selection box.
- Added optional debug window (off by default) listing objects in current selection and clipboard counts.
- Added clipboard copy/paste:
  - Key 3 copies placed building objects in selection.
  - Key 4 pastes copied objects relative to player position.
- Added variant-aware paste support.
- Added inventory gate on paste:
  - Requires matching building items (ToolBuilder stacks) in inventory.
  - Blocks paste if missing items and shows exact missing counts popup.
  - Consumes required items from inventory when paste succeeds.